{"tid":1979820,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"420","createTime":"2020-04-19T16:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T10:01:31.000Z","uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2d106ac417da32a1245a4fbff4abc2434f68cc67","tid":1979820,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"希望香港政府早日打擊非法大麻，避免再有會員受到荼毒🙏🏿🙏🏿"},{"pid":"7cede33162091853079a1a46dac19a0a8c506300","tid":1979820,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:44:08.000Z","msg":"英超球隊阿仙奴領隊雲加（Ars&egrave;ne Wenger）今日（4月20日）發聲明，指在今季結束後離任。&nbsp; 雲加透過阿仙奴官方網站發聲明，指經過深思熟慮，並與球會商量之後，認為在今季結束後是適當時候退下。他對球會的職員、球員、管理層及球迷致謝。&nbsp; 68歲的雲加自1996年起執教阿仙奴，至今已22年，是英超在任時間最長的領隊，他曾帶領「兵工廠」3奪英超冠軍，7次贏得足總盃，惟未曾揚威歐聯。&nbsp; 近年阿仙奴戰績下滑，上季未能殺入英超前4，今季亦未見起色，如今只期望透過贏得今屆歐霸盃，去爭取來屆歐聯資格。 &nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/article/04-20-2018/45343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F04-20-2018%2F45343&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWuxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=fe338f5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/article/04-20-2018/45343</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020"},{"pid":"e655e704fd0f8886b3a7ae5bc679e6eb3ee0c537","tid":1979820,"uid":19923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d106ac417da32a1245a4fbff4abc2434f68cc67","tid":1979820,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:39:48.000Z","msg":"希望香港政府早日打擊非法大麻，避免再有會員受到荼毒🙏🏿🙏🏿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"有合法既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}